	(text "LoRa Telemetry TX - RF board (E22 + Pixhawk connector)\nStacks directly on top of the main board (DevKitC-1+power): J4\n(male header, TX_Connectors sheet) is mounted on this board's\nBACK side in the PCB layout, plugging down into main's female\nsocket - board sits right-side-up, nothing flipped. Config\nbutton + link LED are broken out via jumper wires (J5) since\nthey need to stay human-accessible once stacked." (at 12.7 70 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))) (uuid "4b8642a4-a04b-4bf3-8825-918f55b6cb2b"))
